<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
            <p>Last updated: December 19, 2024</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
            <p>Time with Kids (the "App") is an application for recording and managing precious time with your children. We respect our users' privacy and are committed to protecting personal information.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
            <h3>2.1 Information Recorded in the App</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Activity records with children (time, category, notes, etc.)</li>
                <li>Set goals and progress status</li>
                <li>App usage statistics (stored locally only)</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h3>2.2 Information We Do Not Collect</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Personally identifiable information (name, address, phone number, etc.)</li>
                <li>Location information</li>
                <li>Contact information</li>
                <li>Photos or videos</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>3. Data Storage and Management</h2>
            <p>All data recorded in this app is stored locally on your device. Data is not transmitted to external servers.</p>
            
            <h3>3.1 Data Backup</h3>
            <p>Data may be stored in cloud services such as iCloud only when users explicitly use the backup feature. In this case, data is encrypted before storage.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>4. Information Sharing with Third Parties</h2>
            <p>We do not share users' personal information with third parties except in the following cases:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>When required by law</li>
                <li>When users have given explicit consent</li>
                <li>Anonymized statistical data for app improvement (only information that cannot identify individuals)</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>5. Data Deletion</h2>
            <p>When the app is deleted, all data stored on the device will be deleted. You can also manually delete data from the app settings.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>6. Children's Privacy</h2>
            <p>This app does not intentionally collect personal information from children under 13. If children under 13 use the app, please use it under parental supervision.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>7. Changes to Privacy Policy</h2>
            <p>This privacy policy may be updated as necessary. If there are significant changes, we will notify you within the app.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>8. Contact Us</h2>
            <p>If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at:</p>
            <p>Email: support@santamaruapp.com</p>
            <p>Support Form: <a href="support-en.html">Contact Form</a></p>
        </div>

